org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.system

Class Deadline

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qualcomm.robotcore.util.ElapsedTime
      • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.system.Deadline

  • public class Deadline
extends ElapsedTime
    Deadline enhances ElapsedTime with an explicit duration. A Deadline can also be cancelled, causing it to expire earlier than it originally would have.
